##

=============================
eZ Accelerator extension NEWS
=============================

-------
History
-------

v1.3 (01.10.2011)
-----------------
- Compatibility and migration to Varnish 3
- Removing of statistic features due to Varnish 3 
	- In Varnish 3, the "stats" command no longer exists
- Rename eZ Nova Rnish to eZ Accelerator
- PHP docs
- Replacing the purge system on BAN console to the HTTP protocol for more velocity
- Restructuring of extension subtree for eZ Market certification
- Default Varnish Error page override

v1.2 (30.07.2011)
-----------------
- Refactoring of the core system for the 4.5
	- Removing kernel Overrides
	- Using the new system of Event Dispatching
	- 3 cluster subclasses to manage the StaleCache (possible since useStaleCache variable is no longer private)
- Added a daemon to asynchronously clear varnish
	- daemon php
	-  Debian startup script
- Statistics 
	- Real Time (Hits Misses, Memory)
	- Historical (via a cronjob)	
	
v1.1 (15.06.2011)
-----------------
- System url purge refactoring, now, we flag all pages with a node_id header in Varnish, and the Varnish purge is made on the node_id header.
- Add a template operator to add the header

